In a few weeks, the narrative of Russian official propaganda on the United States has radically changed. If before they were the enemy who wanted to destroy the Federation using as a launch ramp Ukraine and Europe and with which, for this reason, Moscow embarked on a "holy war", today the US with Trump are, if not an ally, at least one of the countries with which they share a number of values.&nbsp;
When Putin publicly commented on the proposal of temporary truce in Ukraine, he thanked the American president by comparing his efforts for peace to what other world leaders like Chinese Xi Jinping > and Indian Narendra Modi> are doing. The role of the enemy trying to contain Russia has passed to the United Kingdom, told the Reuters three Russian officials, one of whom has clearly observed that London is "fearing chaos and war" in Ukraine.
&nbsp;
